      • PROXY_BACKEND_QUERY_FETCH_SIZE

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_BACKEND_QUERY_FETCH_SIZE
        Proxy backend query fetch size. A larger value may increase the memory usage of ShardingSphere Proxy. The default value is -1, which means set the minimum value for different JDBC drivers.

      • PROXY_FRONTEND_EXECUTOR_SIZE

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_FRONTEND_EXECUTOR_SIZE
        Proxy frontend executor size. The default value is 0, which means let Netty decide.

      • PROXY_BACKEND_EXECUTOR_SUITABLE

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_BACKEND_EXECUTOR_SUITABLE
        Available options of proxy backend executor suitable: OLAP(default), OLTP. The OLTP option may reduce time cost of writing packets to client, but it may increase the latency of SQL execution and block other clients if client connections are more than PROXY_FRONTEND_EXECUTOR_SIZE, especially executing slow SQL.

      • PROXY_FRONTEND_MAX_CONNECTIONS

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_FRONTEND_MAX_CONNECTIONS
        Less than or equal to 0 means no limitation.

      • PROXY_MYSQL_DEFAULT_VERSION

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_MYSQL_DEFAULT_VERSION
        Proxy MySQL default version.

      • PROXY_DEFAULT_PORT

        public static final ConfigurationPropertyKey PROXY_DEFAULT_PORT
